    To reset your password, you need to follow this link and type a new password.
    <a href="{{ resettingLink }}">Reset password</a>

    If the link doesn't work, thanks to copy/paste this link in your browser:
    {{ resettingLink }}
</p>

<p>
    Best regards,<br>
    The Collection Manager team
</p>
